<p>Hello,</p>

<p>
  You still need to finish onboarding before <%= @event.name %> can pay you for the <%= @position.title %> position.
  <% if @next_step.present? %>
    Your next step is: <strong><%= @next_step[:label] %></strong>.
  <% end %>
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Click here", onboarding_payroll_position_url(@position) %> to review your position and complete any remaining steps, including submitting your tax form (W-9 / W-8BEN) and configuring your payout method.
</p>

<p>
  If you have any questions, please contact <%= @event.name %>.
</p>

<p>
  Sincerely,
  <br><br>
  The HCB Team
</p>

<p><i class="muted"><%= @event.name %> is fiscally sponsored by The Hack Foundation (d.b.a. HCB), a 501(c)(3) nonprofit (EIN: 81-2908499).</i></p>
